44
00:04:41,379 --> 00:04:45,759
Like the story between the Hengdao Sect and the Sea of Clear Skies.

45
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:51,459
And why you, as the guardian of Mist Soul, are so interested in Rehai?

46
00:04:55,360 --> 00:05:01,999
