47
00:05:13,459 --> 00:05:17,800
I hope... we can work well together.

48
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:28,119
This is... the key ring of Rehai?

49
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:35,960
This key ring of Rehai is an important item against Zhu Yu.

50
00:05:37,179 --> 00:05:40,580
It's made from the dragon bone of Guixu.

51
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:46,539
Back then Shennong forged the Rehai key ring with dragon bone.

52
00:05:46,539 --> 00:05:51,240
I duplicated it to confuse Zhu Yu.

53
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:58,200
Interesting... The key ring of Rehai can be copied.

54
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,920
Cang Feng.

55
00:06:01,130 --> 00:06:02,870
Keep it safe.

56
00:06:06,119 --> 00:06:10,899
Cang Feng, you're also a guardian of Rehai now.

57
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,376
I appreciate it.

58
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:24,340
Next time we meet, we'll discuss how to deal with Zhu Yu.

59
00:06:24,340 --> 00:06:28,000
I've agreed to side with you against Zhu Yu.

60
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:34,360
In exchange, shouldn't you show me some sincerity, Commander Ying?

61
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:41,059
I wonder if the way to remove the binding shows enough sincerity.

62
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,040
Of course, it can.

63
00:06:47,619 --> 00:06:50,759
Bloodbinding the spring defies the will of heaven.

64
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:56,020
It can only be removed with the help of a kin's blood.

65
00:06:56,020 --> 00:07:00,939
The closer the kin, the more likely it'll succeed.

66
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:04,379
Blood of a close kin.

67
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:10,860
There's yet another way.

68
00:07:10,860 --> 00:07:16,400
The blood of the whole clan works the same.

69
00:07:33,379 --> 00:07:38,639
Zhaoyan, you finally came back.

70
00:07:53,599 --> 00:07:56,219
What's with that look?

71
00:07:56,219 --> 00:08:00,059
Did you do something behind my back?

72
00:08:00,059 --> 00:08:04,919
No, Maiming, Miss Ming needs a favor.

73
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:10,900
My master died.

74
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:14,860
I heard that the Nine Springs Dragon Pool can bring back the deceased.

75
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:17,819
I'd like to go there through Rehai.

76
00:08:17,819 --> 00:08:20,180
Miss Luo, I'm hoping you'll help me.

77
00:08:23,439 --> 00:08:25,288
Maiming.

78
00:08:26,779 --> 00:08:29,919
The Dragon Pool has a sentry stationed there.

79
00:08:29,919 --> 00:08:32,480
No one can enter easily.

80
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:36,300
Miss Ming, you don't look well.

81
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:41,219
Why don't you rest tonight and prepare to enter the Dragon Pool tomorrow?

82
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,664
Thank you.

83
00:08:49,119 --> 00:08:52,000
