84
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:54,440
Thank you, Maiming.

85
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,979
I'll go see Xian Qing and the others now.

86
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:05,120
Zhaoyan, I need to speak with you.

87
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:17,859
You told the others about Rehai.

88
00:09:17,859 --> 00:09:21,919
