101
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:32,299
I wanted to use that short time to help the Luo family thrive.

102
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,480
But now...

103
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:44,499
You have limited time because I took your life.

104
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:52,199
