106
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:58,720
Don't you hate me?

107
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:01,176
Maiming.

108
00:11:03,439 --> 00:11:06,160
I've always been steadfast in this.

109
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:11,800
I'd be lying if I said I'd never felt resentment.

110
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:15,500
But since it's decided that I can't live long,

111
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:19,200
I might as well focus on how to live a brilliant life.

112
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:22,800
