122
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:17,560
Appreciate orioles among the flowers.

123
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,600
Appreciate a beauty under the moon.

124
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:23,440
My sister is such a pretty girl.

125
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:30,600
Then, can I change back into my clothes?

126
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:32,800
I'm not really used to this.

127
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:37,200
The ceremony is coming. Our clan people are returning.

128
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:39,800
It's nothing weird to see a new face.

129
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:43,200
Why don't you experience life as a girl?

130
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:48,300
Or is it because you don't like my gift?

131
00:14:58,300 --> 00:15:00,000
Fine then.

