00:18:39,700 --> 00:18:43,000
Zhaoyan really is a girl.

163
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:45,800
Didn't you know that awhile ago?

164
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:48,800
I'm just not used to it.

165
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:51,600
I guess we can't call her Brother Luo anymore.

166
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:55,340
Let's just call her Zhaoyan.

167
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,100
You look beautiful.

168
00:19:21,560 --> 00:19:24,180
Walk... with me.

