170
00:20:16,239 --> 00:20:19,680
Y-You're Miss Luo.

171
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:23,320
Since Zhaoyan trusts you,

172
00:20:23,320 --> 00:20:26,440
I don't have to hide anything anymore.

173
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:28,599
I'm Luo Maiming.

174
00:20:30,479 --> 00:20:34,080
"Miss Luo" became "Master Luo" out of the blue.

175
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:37,359
We have to get used to it.

176
00:20:40,879 --> 00:20:42,759
Where is Zhaoyan?

177
00:20:42,759 --> 00:20:45,080
She fell sick.

178
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:49,200
She's feeling unwell. She told me to get you into Rehai first.

179
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:50,800
How is she doing?

180
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:54,400
It's a chronic problem. She just needs some rest.

181
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:55,900
We know Zhaoyan.

182
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:59,300
She'd come to say goodbye even if she was sick.

183
00:20:59,920 --> 00:21:03,160
I persuaded her to stay and rest.

184
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:06,808
What's wrong, Senior Uncle?

185
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:38,500
Why is Xian Qing gone?

186
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:41,600
Yes, he was right behind us before.

187
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:44,400
I bet he has things to deal with.

188
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:46,200
Let's head to the Dragon Pool first.

189
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:50,600
Yes, let's take care of Senior Gu's issue first and meet them later.

190
00:21:50,600 --> 00:21:52,100
Let's go.

191
00:22:21,700 --> 00:22:23,400
Zhaoyan.

192
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:41,000
Maiming! Maiming, what's going on?

193
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:45,600
Yesterday... a distinguished guest visited.

194
00:22:46,639 --> 00:22:49,360
Guess what he told me?

195
00:22:50,359 --> 00:22:54,760
He told me how to remove the Bloodbinding.

196
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:57,720
Really?

197
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:07,700
Back then, I thought I needed to just sacrifice myself.

198
00:23:07,700 --> 00:23:10,500
But I ended up in an eternal prison,

199
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:14,600
constantly reincarnated and borrowing life from others,

200
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:17,600
living like a walking dead.

201
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:20,000
I know that. I know, Maiming.

202
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:23,300
You have endured torture and suffering from the Luo family all these years.

203
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:26,500
Is there really a way out now?

204
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:33,500
Yes, he said only the blood of the closest kin will work.

205
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:41,400
You... need my blood.

206
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:47,800
Zhaoyan, do you still remember

207
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:52,400
that you live and die with me?

208
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:55,500
I do. Of course.

209
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:59,000
But all you have to do is ask, Maiming.

210
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:00,500
Why did you chain me up?

211
00:24:00,500 --> 00:24:02,800
Because you've changed.

212
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:07,000
You're not the same Zhaoyan anymore.

213
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:13,500
   

214
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:17,720
What's going on?

215
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:22,199
 Intruders. 

216
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,200
Are you the sentry of the Dragon Pool?

217
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:30,400
We're with the guardian of Pureness and heading to the Dragon Pool.

218
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:32,300
Please let us pass.

219
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:36,200
 Guardian of Pureness? 

220
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:40,700
 There's darkness hidden deep down inside this guardian. 

221
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:42,900
What is this...

222
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:45,900
- Miss Ming. 
 - Sister Ming Xiu.

223
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:48,100
Qi, hold tight to me.

224
00:24:48,999 --> 00:24:53,539
 Stay lost in the maze of memories forever. 

225
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:04,300
Where is Xian Qing and the others? You didn't hurt them, did you?

226
00:25:08,560 --> 00:25:11,600
Even now, you're still thinking about him.

227
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:14,500
Where are they, Maiming?

228
00:25:14,500 --> 00:25:16,600
Don't hurt them. Okay?

229
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:21,300
I shouldn't have let you go to Luori Village.

230
00:25:21,300 --> 00:25:24,700
Giving that wolf demon a chance to approach you.

231
00:25:24,700 --> 00:25:27,800
- So you're targeting... 
 - Yes.

232
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:33,300
I'll kill the wolf demon.

233
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:36,900
Are you crazy, Maiming? Are you mad?

234
00:25:36,900 --> 00:25:42,400
What? You're worried about him?

235
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:44,100
Maiming!

236
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:50,259
By the end of the day, you'll be back to how you were.

237
00:26:13,900 --> 00:26:17,700
Xian Qing. Xian Qing, run! He's after you!

238
00:26:17,700 --> 00:26:19,600
You're here.

239
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:23,600
Maiming. Maiming...

240
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:25,900
Maiming... Maiming!

241
00:26:25,900 --> 00:26:27,800
Xian Qing, hurry, go!

242
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:40,500
Luo Maiming, you've always cherished Zhaoyan.

243
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:42,900
And she's done a lot for you.

244
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:47,300
I'm the one you want. Why do you have to do this to her?

245
00:26:47,300 --> 00:26:51,100
We've been keeping each other company for years.

246
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:54,200
But now she only cares about you.

247
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:57,000
In that case, I might as well kill her.

248
00:26:57,960 --> 00:27:01,960
You want to kill her? Did I give you permission?

249
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:13,000
Maiming! Maiming, let him go!

250
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,800
Xian Qing!

251
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:24,800
Maiming, please!

252
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:43,800
Maiming, please let him go!

253
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:45,400
I beg you, don't hurt him!

254
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:47,100
Xian Qing!

255
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,900
I-I'm here...

256
00:27:50,900 --> 00:27:52,700
